author: Alex Patton
title: Internal split rankles House Dems looking for 2018 wins
text:
You are here: Home / US / Internal split rankles House Dems looking for 2018 wins Internal split rankles House Dems looking for 2018 wins February 10, 2017 By Alex Patton 
House Democrats put on a unified show in public this week at their annual retreat, but behind the scenes members of the party were still trying to find a way to bridge their own divides ahead of a 2018 election that could put them back in control of the House or deeper in the hole than before.
